58:20.433 --> 58:22.803
- Mike, you're not gonna be
able to get those doors open.

58:22.803 --> 58:23.733
Not with them on your tail.

58:23.733 --> 58:24.933
- You got a better idea?

58:26.033 --> 58:27.903
(children yelling)

58:27.903 --> 58:28.736
- I'll go too.

58:29.793 --> 58:31.803
Run around the other direction.

58:31.803 --> 58:33.753
Someone has to lock them in
once you're through anyway.

58:33.753 --> 58:34.593
- Peter.

58:34.593 --> 58:35.426
- He's right.

58:37.683 --> 58:38.883
- It's okay. I'll do it.

58:40.233 --> 58:41.066
- Let's go.

58:42.438 --> 58:44.433
(ominous music)

58:44.433 --> 58:45.266
- Mike.

58:46.192 --> 58:48.775
(kids yelling)

58:50.733 --> 58:51.566
Here.

58:53.656 --> 58:55.756
- I thought you said you-
- Just in case.

59:01.148 --> 59:02.153
- All right.

59:02.153 --> 59:04.863
On my count, as soon as I'm through,

59:04.863 --> 59:07.203
Lauren, slam it shut.

59:07.203 --> 59:09.426
When it's clear, Pete, you run for it.

59:10.503 --> 59:11.336
I'll go the long way,

59:11.336 --> 59:13.433
and I'll shout when I
come around the bend.

59:14.793 --> 59:15.933
If the doors aren't open yet-

59:15.933 --> 59:16.766
- They'll be open.

59:16.766 --> 59:19.266
- If they aren't, I'll run another lap.

59:20.343 --> 59:21.486
The mob can't split.

59:22.953 --> 59:24.453
We have to keep them together.

59:25.323 --> 59:26.703
One target.

